name: Experiment Or Die #115
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. This is the 12th letter in The Cool Alphabet, D Is For Dalek, and is kind of a double entendre considering how much time I spend in Dalektown but decided to feature the root inspiration moreso... because you know, I also love me some Doctor Who. 4 scrabble tiles, Edition of 4. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
